---
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Helicon Labs | Engineering Governance</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Helicon Labs builds products for engineering governance and change orchestration. Fleetu helps teams roll out software changes safely and at scale."
    />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Helicon Labs | Engineering Governance" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="We build products that help engineering organizations plan, execute, and audit software change with confidence."
    />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://heliconlabs.dev/en/" />
    <meta property="og:locale" content="en_US" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/og-image.svg" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a1322" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://heliconlabs.dev/en/" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://heliconlabs.dev/en/" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="pt-BR" href="https://heliconlabs.dev/pt-BR/" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="x-default" href="https://heliconlabs.dev/en/" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/heliconlabs-logo.svg" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="wrapper header">
        <div class="topbar">
          <p class="badge">System Status: Online</p>
          <nav class="lang-switch" aria-label="Language selector">
            <a class="lang-pill active" href="/en/" aria-current="page">EN</a>
            <a class="lang-pill" href="/pt-BR/">PT-BR</a>
          </nav>
        </div>
        <h1 class="title">HELICON LABS</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
          We build products for engineering governance, helping software
          organizations plan, execute, and audit change with confidence.
        </p>

        <article class="panel" aria-label="Helicon systems overview">
          <div class="panel-top">
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="dot"></span>
            <span class="panel-title">Helicon Boot Console</span>
          </div>
          <div class="terminal">
            <p class="line l1">&gt; Booting Helicon control plane...</p>
            <p class="line l2">
              &gt; Product spotlight: <strong>Fleetu</strong>
            </p>
            <p class="line l3">
              &gt; Focus: safe change orchestration across repositories
            </p>
            <p class="line l4">&gt; Governance built into every rollout.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <section class="grid" aria-label="company overview">
          <article class="card span-4">
            <h3>What We Do</h3>
            <p>
              We create software that turns large technical change into a reliable,
              governed process for engineering organizations.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card span-4">
            <h3>Fleetu</h3>
            <p>
              Fleetu is our flagship product for orchestrating engineering changes
              across repository fleets with visibility and control.
            </p>
            <a class="card-link" href="https://fleetu.io" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Visit fleetu.io</a>
          </article>

          <article class="card span-4">
            <h3>Who We Work With</h3>
            <p>
              Platform, architecture, and engineering enablement teams responsible
              for cross-repository standards and upgrades.
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="card span-8">
            <h3>How We Operate</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Safety-first rollout design</li>
              <li>Clear ownership and approval flow</li>
              <li>Auditability as a core product capability</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="card span-4">
            <h3>Contact</h3>
            <p>
              hello@heliconlabs.dev
            </p>
            <p>Based in Brazil, building for global engineering teams.</p>
          </article>
        </section>

        <div class="cta">
          <a class="btn primary" href="https://fleetu.io" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Visit Fleetu</a>
          <a class="btn" href="mailto:hello@heliconlabs.dev">Talk to Helicon</a>
        </div>

        <footer class="footer">Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Helicon Labs</footer>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
